            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".)",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The implements.—Or, vessels. The word all is omitted by some MSS., and by the LXX., Syriac, and Arabic. “The holy things of David” are identical with “the silver and the gold and the vessels.”",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "The implements.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Or, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "vessels.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " The word ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "all",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " is omitted by some MSS., and by the LXX., Syriac, and Arabic. “The holy things of David” are identical with “the silver and the gold and the vessels.”",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "THE DEDICATION OF THE TEMPLE (2Chronicles 5:2 to 2Chronicles 7:22).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "THE DEDICATION OF THE TEMPLE",
