  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "CHAPTER 5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "2Ch 5:1. The Dedicated Treasures.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1. Solomon brought in all the things that David his father had dedicated—the immense sums and the store of valuable articles which his father and other generals had reserved and appropriated for the temple (1Ch 22:14; 26:26).The dedicated treasures, 2 Chronicles 5:1. The solemn induction of the ark into the oracle, 2 Chronicles 5:2-10. Glory and praise is sung to God, who appeareth in a cloud, which filled the house, 2 Chronicles 5:11-14.  Or, even (as that particle is oft understood) the silver and the gold,  the remainder of those vast sums mentioned 1 Chronicles 22:14. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "1. Solomon brought in all the things that David his father had dedicated—the immense sums and the store of valuable articles which his father and other generals had reserved and appropriated for the temple (1Ch 22:14; 26:26).The dedicated treasures, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 5:1",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". The solemn induction of the ark into the oracle, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 5:2-10",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Glory and praise is sung to God, who appeareth in a cloud, which filled the house, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 5:11-14",
            "children": []
